{
  "stem": "1415.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the thing is, I was three and a half years in ghettos and concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it started out with the open ghetto, and then, little by little, they concentrated us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at first it was a bigger ghetto, which was one-- one big street in our hometown, was little to begin with.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then it became smaller and smaller, until they just-- they built a camp-- the [GERMAN], and that was small with regular barracks.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because in the ghetto we were still living in people's houses that used to live there because it was a part of town.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when we got to the camp, these were actual barracks that were built specially for us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were wooden barracks, and we slept on-- on-- on like a wooden-- a wooden bunk that was the length of the barrack-- the bunk.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And everybody just slept in a row.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and the bunk was like in-- in the middle, so people slept head to head, head to head, and there was two rows of people.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was the-- that was the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now, from-- from the ghetto is when I finally got into the camp, when I was telling that-- that-- when I related my incident with-- with the SS.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was the entry into the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was my first entry into the concentration camp or hard labor camp of Ostrowiec.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as long as my parents were there, I was very-- I was fine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was fine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- if they were there, then it was OK.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's the only explanation I have as a child.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because if your parents are there, it doesn't matter how devastating or how bad, it's OK, because your parents are there, or even though I was never really with them.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
